OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FA teenager, two men and a woman have
OL,7,Fdied after getting into difficulty
OL,8,Fswimming in open water, bringing the
OL,9,Ftotal number of drownings during the
OL,10,Frecent heatwave to six.
OL,12,FBrody Leach's body was recovered from
OL,13,Fthe River Severn in Shrewsbury,
OL,14,FShropshire, on Saturday morning, West
OL,15,FMercia Police said.
OL,17,FThe force said the 22-year-old was
OL,18,Flast seen alive swimming in the river
OL,19,Fon Friday when he apparently got into
OL,20,Ftrouble.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
