OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FMeanwhile, officers searching for a
OL,7,Fmissing 15-year-old boy last seen in
OL,8,Fthe water at Testwood Lakes near
OL,9,FSouthampton have found a body,
OL,10,FHampshire Police said on Saturday.
OL,12,F"The boy's family have been informed
OL,13,Fand formal identification has taken
OL,14,Fplace. His family are being supported
OL,15,Fby specially-trained officers," the
OL,16,Fforce added.
OL,18,FEssex Police has also confirmed the
OL,19,Fdeath of a 69-year-old man in Clacton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
