OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FOfficers said they were called to a
OL,7,Fmedical emergency in Marine Parade
OL,8,FEast at just after 11am on Friday
OL,9,Fafter reports of a man in difficulty
OL,10,Fin the sea.
OL,12,FThe force said: "Officers, paramedics,
OL,13,Fthe fire service and coastguard all
OL,14,Fattended. Sadly, despite colleagues'
OL,15,Fbest efforts, a 69-year-old man died
OL,16,Fat the scene."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
