OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police said on Saturday
OL,7,Fevening that the body of a woman had
OL,8,Fbeen recovered from a pool in Sandwell
OL,9,FValley Country Park after she went
OL,10,Fmissing in the water just after 4:30pm.
OL,12,FThe force said: "Sadly, nothing could
OL,13,Fbe done to save her and she was
OL,14,Fconfirmed deceased at the scene. Our
OL,15,Fthoughts are with her family at this
OL,16,Ftragic time.
OL,18,F"Her death is not being treated as
OL,19,Fsuspicious at this time and we will be
OL,20,Fliaising with the coroner."
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
