OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FThe four deaths bring the total number
OL,7,Fof water-related fatalities during the
OL,8,Frecent heatwave to six after a 50-year-
OL,9,Fold man was pronounced dead on
OL,10,FWednesday afternoon at Aberavon beach
OL,11,Fon the south coast of Wales.
