OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FEarlier, police said they had
OL,7,Frecovered the body of a teenage boy
OL,8,Ffrom a lake in Syston, Leicestershire,
OL,9,Fafter he went into the water on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,FDuring the May heatwave, at least 15
OL,13,Fpeople, the majority of whom were
OL,14,Fchildren, drowned whilst swimming in
OL,15,Fopen water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
