OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FIt prompted widespread warnings about
OL,7,Fthe dangers of trying to cool off with
OL,8,Fa swim in the sea, lake or river, as
OL,9,Fthe water is often much colder than
OL,10,Fexpected and can cause cold water
OL,11,Fshock syndrome that can prove prove
OL,12,Ffatal.
OL,14,FWednesday was the first of three
OL,15,Fconsecutive days in which the hottest
OL,16,FJune day on record was broken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
