OL,3,CSix die in open water during recent
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FFriday was confirmed by the Met Office
OL,7,Fas the UK's hottest June day on
OL,8,Frecord, with a provisional temperature
OL,9,Fof 37.3C recorded in Santon Downham,
OL,10,FSuffolk, surpassing the high of 36.7C
OL,11,Frecorded in Merryfield, Somerset, on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
